PrecisAmendments to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS, in accordance with Schedule No. 729, which will permit the use of sodium stearoyl-2-lactylate (SSL) as an emulsifier in unstandardized cream-based liquors and the use of the enzyme cellulase in the processing of fruit juices.
